org.flexiblepower.messaging

Interface ConnectionManager.EndpointPort

  • Enclosing interface:
    ConnectionManager

    public static interface ConnectionManager.EndpointPort
    The representation of a Port that was defined on an Endpoint. This can be used to find ConnectionManager.PotentialConnections.
